videos.description: Tommy Stevens runs the read option to perfection and dives across the goal line for the Mississippi State touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Stevens’ TD gives Mississippi State early lead) 2019/12/30

videos.headline: Stevens' TD gives Mississippi State early lead

videos.description: Louisville linebacker Dorian Etheridge is disqualified from the game for kicking Mississippi State TE Geor'quarius Spivey, after Spivey held onto Etheridge's other leg long after the play was over.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Louisville LB ejected for kicking opponent) 2019/12/30

videos.headline: Louisville LB ejected for kicking opponent

videos.description: Louisville QB Micale Cunningham throws a backwards screen pass to Tutu Atwell, who then fires deep to a wide-open Marshon Ford for a 33-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Louisville scores TD on trick play) 2019/12/30

videos.headline: Louisville scores TD on trick play

videos.description: Devante Peete gets behind the Mississippi State secondary and Micale Cunningham hits him for the 24-yard Louisville touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Cunningham, Peete connect for Louisville TD) 2019/12/30

videos.headline: Cunningham, Peete connect for Louisville TD

videos.description: Gary McCrae strips Tommy Stevens and the ball pops right into the arms of Khane Pass, who returns it 31-yards for the Louisville touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Louisville D comes up with scoop-and-score) 2019/12/30

videos.headline: Louisville D comes up with scoop-and-score

videos.description: Micale Cunningham slings a pass to Marshon Ford, who barrels his way into the end zone for his second touchdown of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Ford scores 2nd TD for Louisville) 2019/12/30

videos.headline: Ford scores 2nd TD for Louisville
